/**
 * CRC implementation based on lookup tables
 *
 * The tables are generated by the Python module in "tools/bundle7/crc.py". This
 * script is based on the JavaScript implementation on:
 *
 *     http://www.sunshine2k.de/coding/javascript/crc/crc_js.html
 *
 * This website can also be used to generate the (reflected) lookup tables.
 */

